--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DESCRIPTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This role manages sysstat.

This package provides the sar and iostat commands for Linux. Sar and iostat
enable system monitoring of disk, network, and other IO activity.

For more detailed information on the usage and available configuration options
please consult the following sections.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
USAGE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALL
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: sysstat
       sysstat_state: 'install'

REMOVE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: sysstat
       sysstat_state: 'remove'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VARIABLES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ROLE
  sysstat_state
    Description: Control the state of the role.
    Required   : False
    Value      : Predetermined
    Type       : String
    Default    : 'install'
    Options    :
      Install: 'true' | 'yes' | 'install'
      Remove : 'false' | 'no' | 'remove'

